story.title: Littlefield - Part 9
story.storyDescription: Sarah finds a dead body in the woods and uncovers a dark and deadly mystery.

messages.text: Helena, are you there??
NOBODY HAS COME FOR ME YET!!
HELENA?? ARE YOU THERE??
I’m here, I’m here...
It’s been three hours. I don’t know what to do.
I can’t leave the building. It’s surrounded.
Okay, stay calm.
I can’t fucking stay calm!
Listen, my Dad is in an emergency town meeting.
As soon as he gets out, we’re coming to get you.
You can’t talk to anyone else before that??
Nobody is taking questions from me.
I’ve been trying C, you have to believe me
Where are you?? Where are my parents?? Why aren’t they answering my texts??
We’re at the station.
They took your parents’ cell phones just in case your sister makes contact.
Where are they, can I talk to them through your phone??
They put them in a back room somewhere away from me
Why??
I don’t know. I think they are trying to keep stuff from them.
Keep what from them?!
I don’t think they know what’s actually happening.
How could they NOT
I don’t know, but maybe they don’t want them to panic.
Right now buses are pulling into the police station
For what!?
They are mobilizing part of the community to go to a safe haven up north
I don’t know where yet, that’s what I’m trying to figure out.
Part of the community??
Yeah, they’re not taking everyone.
THEY’RE LEAVING ME FOR DEAD, AREN’T THEY???
Corinne, my father would never leave you for dead. Never.
Who are they taking?? Who is more special than everyone else??
I don’t know how they are gauging it...
but right now it looks like friends and family of the police.
I’m guessing the mayor too
So are they leaving Jared too??
About him
Oh God, don’t tell me he’s dead.
I’m actually not sure right now
Wasn’t he with you in the van??
He was until he stole your parents car...
and drove off to meet that drug guy
WHAT
Yeah...I’m kind of reluctant to say what for because...
I don’t want to get your hopes up
Just say it.
Well, he broke into that barn to find your sister...
But I haven’t heard a word from him since
Oh God, did the drug guy do something to him?
No, he actually...got rid of the drug guy on the way in
what do you mean “get rid of??”
He pushed him out of the car. The eaters got him
You’re calling them the eaters??
Jared coined the phrase.
Anyway - I don’t know where any of them are right now...
but you can rest assured that someone is looking for your sister
What if he’s dead?? What if they’re both dead?
Don’t go there yet.
Wait...the meeting just got out. I’m going to go talk to my Dad
Hold on
Please...hurry...they’re trying to break through the window
What’s he saying?
H?
Helena??
Hi...
So is he sending someone??
I’m going to go find your parents
Okay, but are they sending someone??
I’m going to try to break out of here with them to get you
What???
I don’t want to lie to you...he told me to lie to you, but I can’t
Just fucking say it.
When I asked my Dad what they were doing...
he leaned in and said that they can’t send anyone....it’s getting too bad
WHAT???
As long as your parents drive, we’ll be there.
I’ll stop back at my house and get my Dad’s guns, and we’ll be there
Your Dad wanted to just leave me here??
Hold on, I’m finding them...
If it’s getting too bad...
Maybe you should just leave me here
No! That’s not happening!
I don’t want to put you or my family in danger.
And I don’t want them to miss the bus to safety
Stop trying to be a martyr. I just found them
Can I talk to them?? What are they saying?
Helena?? What’s happening??
FUCK FUCK FUCK
We just tried to leave and they wouldn’t let us!!!!
Listen, the second Jared texts me I’ll send him over to you
Corinne??
Can I please talk to my Dad
They just separated us again
Oh my God, they’re getting through the window. One just pushed it’s arm in!!
Tell my family that I love them okay??
Can’t you hide somewhere???
Just do it...they’re going to find me...so please
No, you’re going to get out of there!
And I’m going to give you the directions to the safe place
No I’m not...now ’m not...just tell them for me
I’m so sorry Corinne. I’m so sorry
Oh my God...
Someone is leaning on a car horn!! They’re turning around!!!!
What!??!
They’re leaving!!!
Who is it?? Who’s leaning on the horn?
